{"tid":2103303,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"請留意有部分票站只開放其中一日","createTime":"2020-07-11T06:03:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-11T11:39:33.000Z","uid":2110,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"3135cdfe90ee73bd62d266cff378f9f4be35f776","tid":2103303,"uid":2110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T06:03:02.000Z","msg":"如題，請睇清楚自己想去既票部係開邊日<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n投票攻略：<br />\n加快投票流程步驟, 避免輪到你先黎搞造成阻礙<br />\n<br />\n1.睇自己準備去邊個地方投, 再搵返個票站編號<br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/1rTHp9g2UfTax1rQMgJEyQ6CEjHdJUXHw/view\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Ffile%2Fd%2F1rTHp9g2UfTax1rQMgJEyQ6CEjHdJUXHw%2Fview&d=FEUhZFrEoh9TukhHyG%2BZyBURuvs7l%2FVEN9tydxl6KII%3D&h=3a3f53a9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/file/d/1rTHp9g2UfTax1rQMgJEyQ6CEjHdJUXHw/view</a><br />\n<br />\n2. 入去依度輸入票站個號碼<br />\n<a href=\"https://webapp.popvote.hk/onboarding\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwebapp.popvote.hk%2Fonboarding&d=FEUhZFrEoh9TukhHyG%2BZyBURuvs7l%2FVEN9tydxl6KII%3D&h=f7c6f12f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://webapp.popvote.hk/onboarding</a><br />\n<br />\n3. 拎到個QR CODE之後再screen capture , save低<br />\n<br />\n4. 之後再帶住址證明+screen capture+身分證<br />\n去1.揀左嘅票站投票<br />\n<br />\n5. 投超區記得要選「否」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其他資料：<a href=\"https://landing.popvote.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Flanding.popvote.hk%2F&d=FEUhZFrEoh9TukhHyG%2BZyBURuvs7l%2FVEN9tydxl6KII%3D&h=24cdb850\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://landing.popvote.hk/</a>"},{"pid":"22d4e0cbad6f805021d9a7c6b9673b16f38ade68","tid":2103303,"uid":80954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T06:04:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e0fc16c5a86bceedb74cf8cbd18f4ec9a62f841f","tid":2103303,"uid":2110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T06:07:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5175f967603d8cd397e54a8871691